text.section:
Each emergency administrative regulation shall contain a statement of:
The nature of the emergency;
The reasons why an ordinary administrative regulation is not sufficient;
Whether or not the emergency administrative regulation will be replaced by an ordinary administrative regulation;
If the emergency administrative regulation will be replaced by an ordinary administrative regulation, the following statement: "The ordinary administrative regulation [is or is not] identical to this emergency administrative regulation.";
If the emergency administrative regulation will not be replaced by an ordinary administrative regulation, the reasons therefor; and
If applicable, the explanation required by subsection (5) of this section.
